In [3]:
def format_to_unix(date):
    
    #print date
    
    date_list = date.split('-')
    date_list[3] = date_list[3].split(':')

    unix_time = datetime(int(date_list[0]), int(date_list[1]), int(date_list[2]), int(date_list[3][0]), int(date_list[1])).strftime('%s')
    
    year = int(date_list[0])
    month = int(date_list[1])
    day = int(date_list[2])
    
    hour = int(date_list[3][0])
    minute = int(date_list[3][1])
    second = int(date_list[3][2])
          
    date_dt = datetime(year, month, day, hour, minute, second)
        
    unix_time = date_dt.strftime ("%s")
                
    return unix_time

dataframes = []

names = [
    'still',
    'still_music',
    'hand_up',
    'hand_down',
    'walking',
    'running',
    'after_sprint',
    'tapping_fingers',
    'tapping_foot',
    'flexing'
]

for bvp_file in bvp_files:
    dataframes.append(pd.read_csv(bvp_file))
    
bvp_df = pd.concat(dataframes,sort=True, axis=1)
bvp_df.columns = names

# Subplots
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(15,30))

for i, bvp in enumerate(list(bvp_df)):
    ax = fig.add_subplot(len(list(bvp_df)),1,i+1)
    ax.plot(bvp_df[bvp])
    ax.set_title(bvp, fontsize=12)
    
fig.suptitle('BVP Signals from October 25 Lab Session', fontsize=24)
plt.subplots_adjust(hspace = 0.4)
plt.show()

der_1_df = pd.DataFrame()
der_2_df = pd.DataFrame()

dx = 0.001

for i, column in enumerate(list(bvp_df)):
    der_1_df[column] = bvp_df[column].diff()
    
for i, column in enumerate(list(der_1_df)):
    der_2_df[column] = der_1_df[column].diff()

der_1_df_small = der_1_df.iloc[2000:3000,:]
der_2_df_small = der_2_df.iloc[2000:3000,:]
